		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/05/add-another-to-the-trilogy-list/" rel="bookmark">Add another to the trilogy list</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>It&#8217;s not every year that you see two great trilogies come to live. Heck, it&#8217;s three so far! Today, thanks to my friend Robyn, we saw the Shrek trilogy come to life.<br />
I have to say, while it might not be as good as the second, it was still really solid.<br />
