<article id="post-608" class="post-608 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-pop-culture category-technology">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/01/disbelieving-drm-and-copy-protection/" rel="bookmark">Disbelieving DRM and copy protection</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I don&#8217;t believe in copy protection, like I don&#8217;t believe in the Easter Bunny or Jimmy Hoffa. It&#8217;s a myth that people cling to like a squirrel to a curtain, which is to say they have to because they are unable to see any other way out of the problem.<br />
I pity those people. Living under that rock must get awfully lonesome.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/01/disbelieving-drm-and-copy-protection/#more-608" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Disbelieving DRM and copy protection&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/01/disbelieving-drm-and-copy-protection/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2007-01-15T22:23:30-07:00">15 January 2007</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/pop-culture/" rel="category tag">Pop Culture</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/technology/" rel="category tag">Technology</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/01/disbelieving-drm-and-copy-protection/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Disbelieving DRM and copy protection</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
